org.knime.core.node.workflow

Class WizardExecutionController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.core.node.workflow.ExecutionController
      • org.knime.core.node.workflow.WizardExecutionController

  • public final class WizardExecutionController
extends ExecutionController
    A utility class received from the workflow manager that allows stepping back and forth in a wizard execution. USed for the 2nd generation wizard execution based on SubNodes.

    Do not use, no public API.

    Since:
    2.10
    Author:
    Bernd Wiswedel, KNIME.com, Zurich, Switzerland, Christian Albrecht, KNIME.com, Zurich, Switzerland
